<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12127b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12127b">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12127b"> 127(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> offer holy water at / church door</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">A l&apos;ordinaire, les offices &eacute;taient moins solennels. Et lorsqu&apos;ils entraient le soir, pour chanter Complies, deux par deux, en se donnant de l&apos;eau b&eacute;nite, dans la vaste nef mal &eacute;clair&eacute;e par un maigre luminaire, les fr&egrave;res &eacute;tudiants de Toulouse devaient avoir une sensation de frisson et d&apos;effroi. <br><font color="green">[Normally, the offices were less solemn. And when they entered in the evening, to sing Compline, two by two, offering each other holy water, in the vast nave not very well lit with a small light, the monk students of Toulouse must have had a shudder of thrill and fear.]</font> <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 21</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
